name: PSYCLOPP SD #03
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters.

This is a special character edition not available for purchase and is a gift from me to those early adopters of my URTH series. An official release version of Psyclopp will be available in the near future.
